## puppet-fluentd changelog

Release notes for the srfmmz/puppet-fluentd module.

------------------------------------------

#### 0.1.4 - 2014/07/21

* added filter functionality
* restart td-agent daemon after config change
* configfile syntax fix for td-agent v2 

#### 0.1.3 - 2014/07/06

Please update to get the new repository of Treasuredata.

Detailed Changes:

* FEATURE : added time_format for source configuration
* CHANGE : Added new treasuredata repositories.
  - for more info see here : https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/fluentd/46FnWIoLTrU
* CHANGE : Restart td-agent when config changed
* FEATURE : Startetd this changelog 